# Survival analysis


df_sau$survival <- Surv(event = df_sau$inhibition_sau, time = df_sau$log_nas_media, type="right")

kmsurv_sau_1 <- survfit(survival ~ case_control , data = df_sau)

survplots <- list()

km_1 <- ggsurvplot(kmsurv_sau_1, data = df_sau,  title = "Staphylococcus aureus", conf.int = F,risk.table = F, surv.plot.height = 5, legend.labs = c("Control","Case"), ggtheme = theme_classic(),legend.title="Case control status",ylim=c(0,1),xlim=c(min(df_sau$log_nas_media),max(df_sau$log_nas_media)),xlab="NASM (log10) CFU/mL",ylab="% Staphylococcus aureus growth",censor=F,palette = c("#009999","#990000"))
